videos.description: QB Woody Barrett airs one out to WR Isaiah McKoy, who stays on his feet and gives the Golden Flashes a 7-0 lead just 10 seconds into the game.
videos.headline: Kent State strikes for 75-yard TD pass on first play of game

videos.description: QB Woody Barrett is on target to WR Mike Carrigan in the back of the end zone as the Golden Flashes continue their fast start against Ohio.
videos.headline: Kent State doubles lead with 1-yard TD pass

videos.description: RB A.J. Ouellette finds an opening and cruises across the goal line to cut the Kent State lead to 14-7.
videos.headline: Ohio responds with 1-yard TD run after impressive drive

videos.description: Woody Barrett misfires a deep ball, but makes a big hit to jar the ball free from DB Marlin Brooks and recover possession.
videos.headline: Kent State QB throws INT, gets ball back with forced fumble

videos.description: QB Nathan Rourke goes over the top to WR Andrew Meyer, who outruns the defense and trims Kent State's lead to 20-14.
videos.headline: Ohio narrows deficit with 59-yard TD pass

videos.description: RB A.J. Ouellette keeps his feet and pushes across the goal line to cut the Golden Flashes' lead to 23-21.
videos.headline: Ohio inches closer with 5-yard TD run

videos.description: QB Nathan Rourke keeps it himself and fights to the end zone, giving the Bobcats a 27-26 lead over Kent State with less than two minutes left.
videos.headline: Ohio takes lead late in 4th quarter
